Sure, here are some examples:

1. *Ponosni* smo na našu zemlju. (We are *proud* of our country.)
2. Ona je uvijek bila *ponosna* na svoje dostignuće. (She has always been *proud* of her achievement.)
3. Ja sam *ponosan* na tebe zbog tvog truda. (I am *proud* of you for your effort.)
4. Njihov *ponos* je bio povrijeđen kada su izgubili utakmicu. (Their *pride* was hurt when they lost the game.)
5. Izraz lica mu je bio pun *ponosa* nakon dobijanja nagrade. (His expression was full of *pride* after receiving the award.)
6. Pogledaj koliko *ponosnih* ljudi okružuje predsjednika. (Look at how many *proud* people surround the president.)
7. Deca su *ponos* svojih roditelja. (Children are their parents' *pride*.)
8. Oni su *ponosno* predstavili svoj novi proizvod na sajmu. (They *proudly* presented their new product at the fair.)
9. Osjećala se *ponosno* kada je prvi put stala na pozornicu. (She felt *proud* when she first stepped onto the stage.)
10. *Ponosni* smo što smo dio ove zajednice. (We are *proud* to be a part of this community.)